{"TopicId":67982,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[0.23.5] Simple Trim Indicators","CreatedByName":"dazoe","CreatedById":100450,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:06:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"dazoe","CreatedById":100450,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:06:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHello,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E So, someone requested Trim Indicators a while ago. So, um, I created this. Hope people like it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EInstallation...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EExtract dll into Plugins or GameData directory.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/6ozDhPrWKy919Qqko4pnGyUq0AR50.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00226ozDhPrWKy919Qqko4pnGyUq0AR50.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/trimindicators/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceport Download\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/dazoe/KSP-TrimIndicators\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESource @ GitHub\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELicense: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/dazoe/KSP-TrimIndicators/blob/master/LICENSE\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMIT\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-04-04T04:38:44Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2014 04:38  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by dazoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KvickFlygarn87","CreatedById":76314,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:33:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs license in download?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, pics or no clicks.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoneyFox","CreatedById":19237,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:37:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELike this idea...if it can be dragged by mouse that will be even better.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dirt_Merchant","CreatedById":69465,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:38:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo simple, yet so valuable. Thank you! Also yes, if they could be mouse drag-able for trim adjustment, that\u0027d be rad!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RED-404","CreatedById":107573,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:40:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI told him to upload a pic via TS and yes the license is in the download.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cl.ly/image/1V3G0Y2c1x1S/Image%202014-04-03%20at%2011.38.30%20PM.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Image%202014-04-03%20at%2011.38.30%20PM.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dazoe","CreatedById":100450,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:42:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDragging by mouse would be much more involved. To make this i simply duplicated the indicators that were already there and scaled them and changed the values they displayed. To make it dragable I\u0027d have to add quite a bit more to it.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RED-404","CreatedById":107573,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:42:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDouble post didn\u0027t realize this was moderated and thought the forum glitches.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-04-04T06:06:04Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2014 06:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by RED-404\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Espelling and double post\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T04:51:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks great. Simple and very useful, like all the best mods.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rottielover","CreatedById":73403,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T05:45:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022White Owl\u0022 data-cite=\u0022White Owl\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELooks great. Simple and very useful, like all the best mods.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2nd that!! Along with \u0022why is this not stock?\u0022 \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMany thousand thank you\u0027s for this mod.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KvickFlygarn87","CreatedById":76314,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T06:35:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlso, if you don\u0027t touch the controls and disable SAS, you\u0027ll see where the trim is.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"anarkhon","CreatedById":22469,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T06:36:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis need to be stock.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kiwiak","CreatedById":82796,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T06:48:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI predict that for few net months (years?) this will be bumped with \u0022why no stock?!\u0022 posts \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E like selectroot.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sethnizzle","CreatedById":22985,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T07:46:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI havent used the trim controls (even though I have them hot keyed to my G-keys) since the new SAS. But this is a really great mod. Agreed this should be stock. Great work.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Horus","CreatedById":99705,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T08:14:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFinally, a no-more-guess visual trim info! Thanks!!!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"skykooler","CreatedById":60459,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T15:51:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAwesome! This will come in so handy every time I accidentally set trim on my craft and can\u0027t tell why it\u0027s spinning!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starstrider42","CreatedById":104043,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T16:08:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYay! The lack of any indicator was the main reason I avoided using trim in my aircraft.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"curiousepic","CreatedById":60039,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T18:06:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENow if only we could clear trim on a per-axis basis...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Amaroq","CreatedById":57607,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T18:28:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMan, and I \u003Cstrong\u003Ejust\u003C/strong\u003E learned how to set trim, too! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NathanKell","CreatedById":75006,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T03:31:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVery nice!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"frizzank","CreatedById":57210,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T03:51:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for doing this...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FenrirWolf","CreatedById":72121,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T08:20:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe only request I have is that you give it a sub-folder in GameData like all the other mods, just for organizational purposes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AndreyATGB","CreatedById":62674,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T09:29:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FenrirWolf\u0022 data-cite=\u0022FenrirWolf\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThe only request I have is that you give it a sub-folder in GameData like all the other mods, just for organizational purposes.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESince it\u0027s just a DLL, you can probably move it in a folder yourself and it would still work. The only time plugins don\u0027t work when moved is when they\u0027re hard coded to load something from a specific folder.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FenrirWolf","CreatedById":72121,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-08T00:25:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECool, thanks for pointing that out\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ArcFurnace","CreatedById":109240,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-05-09T17:02:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI created a \u0022TrimIndicators\u0022 folder to stick the .dll into, it works fine. Thanks for this handy little mod, dazoe!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zeroignite","CreatedById":1377,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-05-09T18:51:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI may use trim now!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}